Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:23.25,OP EN,,0,0,0,,I will forever embrace the destiny we swore upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:26.94,OP EN,,0,0,0,,Now that we're here I won't run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:32.58,OP EN,,0,0,0,,You and I; we'll face the here and now together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:48.16,OP EN,,0,0,0,,The seasons we shared together when we were young;
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:53.87,OP EN,,0,0,0,,we chatted about the future amid our laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:21:02.08,OP EN,,0,0,0,,The cruel time apart snatched everything away;
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:06.24,OP EN,,0,0,0,,including the smile you had that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:09.07,OP EN,,0,0,0,,The vivid memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:11.97,OP EN,,0,0,0,,and your gaze at that instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:16.04,OP EN,,0,0,0,,kept us from speaking ill of one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:21.65,OP EN,,0,0,0,,To take back that frozen time, I will now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:25.41,OP EN,,0,0,0,,surpass the you that's passing me by
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:27.69,OP EN,,0,0,0,,with the bonds from that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:33.76,OP EN,,0,0,0,,I will forever embrace the destiny we swore upon,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:37.67,OP EN,,0,0,0,,putting it all into this strike for a new future!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:40.18,OP EN,,0,0,0,,I won't be afraid anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:43.09,OP EN,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Together, you and I!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:23.25,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,誓い合った　運命　ずっと　胸に　抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:26.94,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,ここまで　来た　もう　逃げはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:32.58,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,今と　向き合うために　行こう、　君と　共に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:48.16,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,幼い日　二人で　過ごした　季節
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:53.87,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,未来　語って　笑いあっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:21:02.08,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,離れていた　時間は　無情なほどに　全て　奪った
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:06.24,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,あの日の　君の　笑顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:09.07,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,鮮明な　記憶と
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:11.97,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,刹那の　眼差しが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:16.04,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,腐さしては　二人　言葉を　避ける
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:21.65,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,止まっていた　時間を　取り戻すために　今
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:25.41,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,すれ違って　君を　超える　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:27.69,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,あの日の　絆で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:33.76,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,誓い合った　運命　ずっと　胸に　抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:37.67,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,全て込める THE NEW FUTURE STRIKE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:40.18,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,何も　恐れはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:43.09,OP漢字,,0,0,0,,行こう、　君と　共に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:32.69,ED EN,,0,0,0,,I gaze at your trembling back as you yearn to become stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:36.83,ED EN,,0,0,0,,making a wish on the cold and the blooming flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:40.35,ED EN,,0,0,0,,to allow me to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:46.96,ED EN,,0,0,0,,I realized I couldn't walk those sleepless streets alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:54.47,ED EN,,0,0,0,,but the warmth from the hands of that special someone softened my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:57.82,ED EN,,0,0,0,,I'm soaring now; no longer lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:03.66,ED EN,,0,0,0,,If I gaze up, the endless stars are guiding us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:12.22,ED EN,,0,0,0,,Within the spirals of time, a sprouting hope spins
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.22,0:23:15.74,ED EN,,0,0,0,,becoming a seed of courage for those sad memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:19.23,ED EN,,0,0,0,,and dying them in the light of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:22.78,ED EN,,0,0,0,,I'll show you I have the key to your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:26.29,ED EN,,0,0,0,,as I open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:29.78,ED EN,,0,0,0,,Drawing the map that leads to our shining future
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:37.18,ED EN,,0,0,0,,lies within our hands clasped tightly together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:32.69,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,強くなりたいと震えている背中を見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:36.83,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,凛と咲く花に願い事　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:40.35,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,君のことを守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:46.96,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,一人じゃ歩けないと気付いた　眠れない街で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:54.47,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,大切な人の手の温もりで　僕は優しくなれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:57.82,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,飛び立てるよ　もう迷わない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:03.66,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,見上げれば　果て無い星を　僕らは照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:12.22,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,巡り巡るときの中で　芽生えた願い紡いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.22,0:23:15.74,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,悲しみの記憶は　勇気の種になる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:19.23,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,希望の光　染まるいて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:22.78,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,閉じ込めた心の鍵は　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:26.29,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,僕が開けてみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:29.78,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,描き出す未来の地図よ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:37.18,ED漢字,,0,0,0,,強く輝いて　繋いだ手の中で
